To build and install lgmon:

        for rpm
        ./autogen.sh --program-suffix=<Printer Model Name>
        for deb
        ./autogen.sh --prefix=/usr --enable-progpath=/usr/bin --program-suffix=<Printer Model Name>
        make
        make install

To build and install lgmon with AUTOCONF

You can set the following <Printer Model Name>.
            e610
            mx390
            mx450
            mx520
            mx720
            mx920

Example for building the mx920 lgmon with the new automake and autoconf:
        for rpm
        ./autogen.sh --program-suffix=mx920
        for deb
        ./autogen.sh --prefix=/usr --enable-progpath=/usr/bin --program-suffix=mx920
        make
        make install

